{
  "stem": "4753.10",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was very often air raids at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was very sick then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had typhus.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I wouldn't stay inside in the barracks, because that meant I stayed there and never come out alive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when I was cleaning, I noticed a hole on the ground that was a shelter, an opening in to a shelter.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I walked down there, and there was a couch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I laid down and fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I dreamed about my mother calling me, telling me that my father is calling.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I should go to my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't want to go because I was so cozy and warm, but naturally I did go when my mother repeated it the second time that I should go.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I came out from the hole, I saw the whole city completely empty-- airplane flying above the city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never was so happy than then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bombs falling from the plane, and I was really starting to dance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew the rest of the people are in the church where the SS men always took us in case of air raids.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was half-bombed already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The SS men all disappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They never were around when there was an air raid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were in the shelter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when I came to the church, my girlfriend, Gizko, said, where did you go?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know that if the SS men see you, they will shoot you on the spot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But-- What kind of significance did that dream have for you?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, my mother saved me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
